lead_paragraph: The Queensland Reds sacked Richard Graham on Monday, patience with the underperforming coach finally running out after the 2011 Super Rugby champions opened the new season with successive defeats.

headline.print_headline: Queensland Reds Sack Graham, O'Connor and Stiles Step Up
